      <title>削减股息后，中国资源汽油在一年内最大程度下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/china-resources-gas-falls-most-in-a-year-after-cutting-dividend</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在公用事业遗漏了盈利估计之后，中国资源天然气集团有限公司的股票下跌了一年，并宣布将降低其股息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/china-resources-gas-falls-most-in-a-year-after-cutting-dividend</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 02:09:56 GMT</pubDate>
