    <item>
      <title>中国工厂活动在预期特朗普关税之前扩大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/china-factory-activity-expands-before-expected-trump-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国的工厂活动在三月份继续扩大，这是全球第二经济体的欢迎新闻，此前美国的关税可能会进一步加剧贸易关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/china-factory-activity-expands-before-expected-trump-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 01:33:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着救援队的到来，缅甸地震死亡人数上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-31/myanmar-quake-death-toll-rises-as-rescue-teams-arrive-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五袭击缅甸的强大地震至少造成了1,600人死亡，据报道，该国第二大城市曼德勒报道了广泛的损失。国际救援队已经到达，以协助寻找幸存者。彭博的Margo Towie提供了更多细节。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-03-31/myanmar-quake-death-toll-rises-as-rescue-teams-arrive-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 01:14:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本股票暴跌，因为美国关税担心会击中出口商股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/japanese-shares-plunge-as-us-tariff-worries-hit-exporter-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本股票跌落，使Nikkei的股票规格在2020年3月以来最糟糕的季度，因为出口商和与芯片有关的股票对全球贸易战的担忧滑落。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/japanese-shares-plunge-as-us-tariff-worries-hit-exporter-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 01:04:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国第二钢制造商的年损失近10亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/china-s-no-2-steelmaker-makes-annual-loss-of-nearly-1-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Angang Steel Co Ltd.是中国第二大钢铁制造商的上市部门，去年亏损了近10亿美元，突显了该行业的洪水条件，因为需求降低和价格涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/china-s-no-2-steelmaker-makes-annual-loss-of-nearly-1-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 01:02:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>害虫，啮齿动物的恐惧继续拖下Zensho股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/pest-rodent-fears-continue-to-drag-down-zensho-shares</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Zensho Holdings Co.的股价下跌了6.5％，此前日本餐厅连锁店表示，在多次食品污染事件发生后，它将暂时关闭其大多数Sukiya商店。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/pest-rodent-fears-continue-to-drag-down-zensho-shares</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 00:38:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当交易者权衡特朗普对俄罗斯处罚的威胁时，石油波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analytics-for-march-31</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果市场权衡唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）对俄罗斯原油的新惩罚威胁，如果他的对手弗拉基米尔·普京（Vladimir Putin）拒绝与乌克兰的停火，石油发生了变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analytics-for-march-31</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 23:20:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>监管机构在主要澳大利亚交易所的旗帜合规性缺陷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/regulators-flag-serious-compliance-issues-at-australian-exchange</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚的市场监管机构和中央银行确定了与贸易解决方案有关的交换运营商ASX Ltd.的严重问题，他们说需要立即采取行动才能解决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/regulators-flag-serious-compliance-issues-at-australian-exchange</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 22:37:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
